---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Communication"
  description="IC&RC Prevention Specialist Domain 3. Rack cards, fact sheets, social graphics, talking points, and press-release templates."
>
  <header class="page-header">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="page-header__eyebrow">
        <a href="/professionals">← For prevention professionals</a> · IC&amp;RC PS Domain 3
      </p>
      <h1>Communication</h1>
      <p class="page-header__lead">
        Clear, on-message materials for reaching the public, the media, and
        partners — including state-customized versions carrying each state's
        helpline.
      </p>
    </div>
  </header>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container prose">
      <h2>What this domain covers</h2>
      <p>
        One-way information sharing — the most-requested resource type for many
        prevention specialists. Effective communication is plain-language,
        non-stigmatizing, and consistent in how it presents the helpline.
      </p>
      <h2>Resources here (filling in)</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Print-ready rack cards (state-customized)</li>
        <li>One-page fact sheets on key topics</li>
        <li>Social-media graphics sized for major platforms</li>
        <li>Talking points and press-release templates</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        All public messaging anchors to <strong>1-800-MY-RESET</strong> and surfaces
        <strong>988</strong> for crisis, following NCPG and SAMHSA branding guidance.
        Downloadable assets are being produced. All resources are free.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
